    <filename>Program&nbsp;Files&nbsp;(x86)</filename>.
    You can start this utility by running
    <literal>c:\Program&nbsp;Files\Regina\Regina&nbsp;&regversion;\bin\sigcensus.exe</literal>.
   </para>
  </refsect1>

